-- Bankia Agrees to Sell 38.4% Stake in Inversis, Spokesman Says
-- B y   M a n u e l   B a i g o r r i
-- 2013-06-29T12:22:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-29/bankia-agrees-to-sell-38-4-stake-in-inversis-spokesman-says.html
Bankia agrees to sell its stake in
Inversis to Banco de  Madrid , a spokesman for the lender says by
phone today, declining to be identified due to company policy.
* Bankia may release financial details of transaction as early
as July 1 before stock market opens in Madrid, spokesman says
* NOTE: Sabadell to Sell Its 15.15% Banco Inversis Stake for
